=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90caac5380ea3e1609a1ac3014a89ce296266d07","tid":2489031,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2bca67e715e389fae010a2a0b968fb05849c01bc","tid":2489031,"uid":96303,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:06:12.000Z","msg":"tvb個社會責任係抹黑我地尊敬嘅行政長官<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T16:07:27.000Z","msg":"tvb個社會責任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210414/MUCOZHILWBGNPA27QRVO2LMZZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210414%2FMUCOZHILWBGNPA27QRVO2LMZZM%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sGlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=338a2ac3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210414%2FMUCOZHILWBGNPA27QRVO2LMZZM%2F&h=da850888\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210414/MUCOZHILWBGNPA27QRVO2LMZZM/</a>"},{"pid":"1b1b01d9db9db8d089e892f6d37fcfde0c9e2253","tid":2489031,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"382820647c02536b3b747bd594b4b3bfe03bc3f3","tid":2489031,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T15:54:02.000Z","msg":"(維穩責任?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n無綫「2021藝員及電視製作人員訓練班」今日進行面試，無綫副總經理（綜藝、音樂製作及節目）曾志偉、助理總經理（戲劇製作）曾勵珍、助理總經理（藝員管理及發展）樂易玲也有出席。<br />\n<br />\n曾志偉表示無綫久未開放招聘幕後人員，今次收到的2000多份報名表中，有千幾人應徵藝員，幕後剪接、配音、舞蹈員及助導等也有很多人申請。他在台上分享演藝心路歷程時，叫大家不要局限於幕前︰「我第一份工是做電影龍虎舞獅，後來跟編劇學寫劇本，做埋場記，再晉身做副導演，又跟過剪接，最後有機會成為導演，也是我夢寐以求的工作。我之後客串幕前，慢慢成為演員，加入電視台後又當上主持，發覺電視真的很好玩，這行業的確令人着迷，會愈做愈喜歡。<strong>TVB這份工不但可滿足自己興趣，還要肩負社會責任。很多人放工回到家的閒餘時間就是交給TVB，所以要將社會資訊、娛樂及教育傳遞給大家</strong>。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20210414/1618394738201\" data-sr-url=\"http